### Variables — set once, used by all requests below
@BASE_URL = http://localhost:8080
@TOKEN = eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJ0ZW5hbnRfaWQiOiJ0ZW5hbnQtd2FsbWFydC0wMDEiLCJzdWIiOiJ0ZXN0LXVzZXIifQ.placeholder
@CAMPAIGN = camp-spring-sale-2024


### ── 1. CLICKS ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### 1a. Live today-so-far (defaults to midnight UTC → now)
GET {{BASE_URL}}/v1/ad/{{CAMPAIGN}}/clicks
Authorization: Bearer {{TOKEN}}

###

### 1b. Specific time range — last 24 hours (warm tier: Druid)
GET {{BASE_URL}}/v1/ad/{{CAMPAIGN}}/clicks?start=2024-04-01T00:00:00Z&end=2024-04-02T00:00:00Z
Authorization: Bearer {{TOKEN}}

###

### 1c. Historical range — last 7 days (cold tier: Snowflake)
GET {{BASE_URL}}/v1/ad/{{CAMPAIGN}}/clicks?start=2024-03-25T00:00:00Z&end=2024-04-01T00:00:00Z
Authorization: Bearer {{TOKEN}}

###

### 1d. With per-hour time series breakdown
GET {{BASE_URL}}/v1/ad/{{CAMPAIGN}}/clicks?start=2024-04-01T00:00:00Z&end=2024-04-02T00:00:00Z&timeSeries=true
Authorization: Bearer {{TOKEN}}

###

### 1e. Exactly at the 72-hour routing boundary (still routes to Druid)
GET {{BASE_URL}}/v1/ad/{{CAMPAIGN}}/clicks?start=2024-03-30T00:00:00Z&end=2024-04-01T00:00:00Z&timeSeries=true
Authorization: Bearer {{TOKEN}}


### ── 2. IMPRESSIONS ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### 2a. Live today-so-far
GET {{BASE_URL}}/v1/ad/{{CAMPAIGN}}/impressions
Authorization: Bearer {{TOKEN}}

###

### 2b. Specific time range — last 24 hours (warm tier: Druid)
GET {{BASE_URL}}/v1/ad/{{CAMPAIGN}}/impressions?start=2024-04-01T00:00:00Z&end=2024-04-02T00:00:00Z
Authorization: Bearer {{TOKEN}}

###

### 2c. Historical range — last 30 days (cold tier: Snowflake)
GET {{BASE_URL}}/v1/ad/{{CAMPAIGN}}/impressions?start=2024-03-01T00:00:00Z&end=2024-04-01T00:00:00Z
Authorization: Bearer {{TOKEN}}

###

### 2d. With per-hour time series breakdown
GET {{BASE_URL}}/v1/ad/{{CAMPAIGN}}/impressions?start=2024-04-01T00:00:00Z&end=2024-04-02T00:00:00Z&timeSeries=true
Authorization: Bearer {{TOKEN}}


### ── 3. CLICK-TO-BASKET ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### 3a. Live today-so-far
GET {{BASE_URL}}/v1/ad/{{CAMPAIGN}}/clickToBasket
Authorization: Bearer {{TOKEN}}

###

### 3b. Specific time range — last 24 hours (warm tier: Druid)
GET {{BASE_URL}}/v1/ad/{{CAMPAIGN}}/clickToBasket?start=2024-04-01T00:00:00Z&end=2024-04-02T00:00:00Z
Authorization: Bearer {{TOKEN}}

###

### 3c. Historical range — last 90 days (cold tier: Snowflake)
GET {{BASE_URL}}/v1/ad/{{CAMPAIGN}}/clickToBasket?start=2024-01-01T00:00:00Z&end=2024-04-01T00:00:00Z
Authorization: Bearer {{TOKEN}}


### ── 4. ACTUATOR ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### 4a. Health check
GET {{BASE_URL}}/actuator/health

###

### 4b. Prometheus metrics scrape
GET {{BASE_URL}}/actuator/prometheus


### ── 5. SWAGGER / OPENAPI ───────────────────────────────────────────────────

### 5a. Fetch raw OpenAPI JSON spec
# Use this to import the spec into Postman, Insomnia, or any OpenAPI-compatible tool
GET {{BASE_URL}}/v3/api-docs
Accept: application/json

###

### 5b. Verify Swagger UI is reachable
# Opens the HTML shell — paste the URL in a browser for the interactive UI
# http://{{BASE_URL}}/swagger-ui.html
GET {{BASE_URL}}/swagger-ui/index.html


### ── 6. ERROR SCENARIOS ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### 6a. Missing Authorization header → 401
GET {{BASE_URL}}/v1/ad/{{CAMPAIGN}}/clicks

###

### 6b. Expired or tampered token → 401
GET {{BASE_URL}}/v1/ad/{{CAMPAIGN}}/clicks
Authorization: Bearer invalid.token.here

###

### 6c. start supplied without end → 400
GET {{BASE_URL}}/v1/ad/{{CAMPAIGN}}/clicks?start=2024-04-01T00:00:00Z
Authorization: Bearer {{TOKEN}}

###

### 6d. end before start → 400
GET {{BASE_URL}}/v1/ad/{{CAMPAIGN}}/clicks?start=2024-04-02T00:00:00Z&end=2024-04-01T00:00:00Z
Authorization: Bearer {{TOKEN}}

###

### 6e. end equal to start → 400
GET {{BASE_URL}}/v1/ad/{{CAMPAIGN}}/clicks?start=2024-04-01T00:00:00Z&end=2024-04-01T00:00:00Z
Authorization: Bearer {{TOKEN}}
